    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior has multiple large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust patches on the wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips occasionally, so it is recommended for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. It is priced to reflect the extensive repairs needed to return it to reliable operation.",
