    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my errands and road trips. It runs smoothly, looks great, and has clearly been well-loved over the years! If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available now is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal traction. This example is mechanically robust, with documented valve adjustments and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains precise, offering the communicative feedback and analog engagement that defines this chassis. A well-maintained performance icon ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a stunning 2018 BMW M3 finished in Alpine White over Black Extended Merino Leather. This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, showing only minor, expected road wear on the front fascia consistent with careful use. The 19-inch M-Double Spoke wheels are in excellent shape and come wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with significant tread depth remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the carbon fiber trim is free of scratches, and the Merino leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, this M3 is in superb health. It boasts a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed at authorized dealerships. The twin-turbo inline-six pulls strongly and smoothly, while the dual-clutch transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. This model is equipped with the Executive Package, featuring a heated steering wheel, heads-up display, and park distance control. The sale includes two keys, all original owner's manuals, and a clean title. This is a turn-key performance sedan ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a refined interior, the car exhibits consistent care and professional upkeep throughout its history. Every system has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak operational integrity and long-term reliability. Experience the perfect synthesis of performance and value in a vehicle that stands ready for the road ahead.",
      "price": 36500.0,
