    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain is robust, with a recent VANOS overhaul utilizing Viton seals and a comprehensive inspection of the rear subframe mounting points for structural integrity. The factory-spec limited-slip differential provides excellent lock-up, and the suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings to ensure precise turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the valve clearances have been shimmed to spec, and the cooling system has been proactively addressed. A turn-key example for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
